If you find errors, unclear explanations, or want to suggest improvements:
- Open an issue on GitHub
- Specific feedback is most helpful (e.g., "timeline.md Oct 24 dates seem conflicted")
- Suggestions for additional documentation topics welcome

This documentation evolves as understanding deepens - your input helps improve it for future readers.

